# MiMo Orchestrator

> Multi-agent workflow engine powered by **Xiaomi MiMo API** — orchestrate, delegate, and chain AI agents with skills, tools, and persistent memory.

[![License: MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-blue.svg)](https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT)
[![Python 3.9+](https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.9+-green.svg)](https://www.python.org/)
[![Powered by Xiaomi MiMo](https://img.shields.io/badge/Powered%20by-Xiaomi%20MiMo-FF6B35?style=flat-square)](https://platform.xiaomimimo.com/)

---

## What is this?

**MiMo Orchestrator** is a production-ready Python CLI tool and library that lets you:

- **Run autonomous agents** powered by Xiaomi MiMo's large language models
- **Orchestrate multiple agents in parallel** — each agent can be a specialized worker (researcher, coder, reviewer, tester)
- **Chain tasks with dependencies** — the output of agent A becomes context for agent B
- **Register custom tools** — give agents shell access, file I/O, web search, and more
- **Load and execute skills** — reusable behaviour packs with trigger keywords and system prompt additions
- **Stream responses** — real-time token-by-token output for interactive use

Think of it as a lightweight, MiMo-native alternative to LangChain agents + CrewAI, purpose-built for the Xiaomi MiMo ecosystem.

---

## Architecture

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    MiMo Orchestrator                        │
│                                                             │
│  ┌──────────────┐   ┌──────────────┐   ┌──────────────┐   │
│  │   Agent A    │   │   Agent B    │   │   Agent C    │   │
│  │  (research)  │   │  (coding)    │   │ (reviewing)  │   │
│  └──────┬───────┘   └──────┬───────┘   └──────┬───────┘   │
│         │                   │                   │            │
│         └───────────────────┼───────────────────┘            │
│                             │                                │
│              ┌──────────────▼──────────────┐               │
│              │      Tool Registry           │               │
│              │  shell | file | web | search │               │
│              └──────────────────────────────┘               │
│                             │                                │
│              ┌──────────────▼──────────────┐               │
│              │      Skill Manager           │               │
│              │  auto-detect + load skills   │               │
│              └──────────────────────────────┘               │
│                             │                                │
│              ┌──────────────▼──────────────┐               │
│              │      MiMo API Client        │               │
│              │   https://api.xiaomimimo.com │               │
│              └──────────────────────────────┘               │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

