## Project Structure

```
mimo-orchestrator/
├── src/mimo_orchestrator/
│   ├── __init__.py          # Package entry point
│   ├── client.py            # MiMo API client
│   ├── agent.py             # Core Agent class
│   ├── orchestrator.py      # Multi-agent orchestration
│   ├── skill_manager.py     # Skill loading & management
│   ├── tool_registry.py     # Tool registration & execution
│   └── cli.py               # CLI entry points
├── skills/                  # Skill packs (YAML)
│   ├── web-server.yaml
│   └── data-analysis.yaml
├── examples/
│   └── quickstart.py
├── pyproject.toml
├── README.md
└── .env.example
```

